Launches 20 fireballs in a straight line towards the furthest enemy away. Inflicts the following effects to enemies hit by fireballs:
- Cover: Deals 8% damage.
- Covered target: Deals 8% damage and prevents them from moving for 2s.
- Other Enemies: Deals <?1> damage and inflicts them with <d:Burn>, continuously dealing <?2> damage every 4s for 40s.
Fireballs that collide with cover will be blocked and not pass through.

RaidSkill.Name: 王国の守護者
RaidSkill.Desc: Deals 100% damage to enemies in a circular area and inflicts them with <d:Burn>, continuously dealing 90% damage<?1> every 4s for 20s.

RaidSkill.Name: 光が照らす知性
RaidSkill.Desc: Destroys all deployed cover and summons for 20s that moves towards the large ballistas. If the wheel collides with a large ballista, deals damage equal to of the ballista's Max HP. If the wheel collides with deployed cover, it will halt in place while continuously dealing 9.6% Mystic damage to the cover every hit. If a covered target is hit by the wheel they will be unable to move for 1.2s. ※ This skill activates when Chokmah's HP is below 85%

RaidSkill.Name: 夜明けを待つ
RaidSkill.Desc: Destroys all deployed cover and enters a rampage. Normal attack changes to a flame breath attack, continuously dealing 50% damage per hit to enemies in a fan-shaped area. Flames from this attack will deal 3% damage to cover and will be blocked. If a covered target is hit they will be unable to move for 1s. While Chokmah is in a rampage, the following effects are applied: - If Chokmah's Reactor Gauge reaches 0%, it will not enter recovery mode. Instead, the gauge will gradually increase, and the lower the gauge, the faster it will increase. - Increases by 100% while the Reactor Gauge is below 70%. - Removes all stacks of and decreases by 100%. - If an enemy Striker is defeated and retreats, the Reactor Gauge will significantly increase. ※ This skill activates when Chokmah's HP is below 35%

RaidSkill.Name: 不離一体の歯車
RaidSkill.Desc: Continuous damage taken from debuffs also damages Chokmah's Reactor Gauge. Once the gauge reaches 0%, it will enter recovery mode and gradually increase over 20s. (25s cooldown between activations). Each time the Reactor Gauge enters recovery mode, inflicts Chokmah with the following effects: - Decreases by 5000, stacking up to 6 times. - Decreases by 100% for 20s. - Inflicts 1 stack of (max. 3 stacks).

RaidSkill.Name: 知恵の証明
RaidSkill.Desc:
The heat from Chokmah prevents enemies from taking cover, and they cannot attack or use skills on cover.
This does not affect skills that directly grant a covered status to the user.

RaidSkill.Name: 制御装置：バリスタ発射
RaidSkill.Desc: Activates the ballista control device at regular intervals (can be activated a maximum of two times). Once activated, the control device can be attacked using EX Skills, and commands the large ballistas to fire at Chokmah once its HP falls below 1%. (If the large ballistas have been destroyed, they will be unable to fire) Additionally increases all enemy Strikers' Crit Rate to the maximum value and by 1000 for 22s.

RaidSkill.Name: 制御装置：バリスタ
RaidSkill.Desc:
When the ballistas fire, Chokmah is restrained and immediately becomes groggy.
While groggy, increases <d:DamagedRatio> by 50% (does not apply if Chokmah is in a rampage). Additionally removes all stacks of <s:EN0009_UnstableFlame> from Chokmah, further increasing <d:DamagedRatio> while groggy by 25% for each stack removed.
